\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {3}{\ignorespaces ADCU{} audit pipeline. A deletion request is expanded through the provenance graph; the post-deletion system $S_-$ is compared against the clean reference $S_{\mathrm  {clean}}$ via a two-sample distance over a graph-adaptive probe budget, six diagnostic channels localize where any residual dependence is mediated, component interventions attribute it causally, and the audit returns a confidence-bounded decision with a retain-utility check.}}{6}{figure.3}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:adcu_pipeline}{{3}{6}{\method {} audit pipeline. A deletion request is expanded through the provenance graph; the post-deletion system $S_-$ is compared against the clean reference $S_{\mathrm {clean}}$ via a two-sample distance over a graph-adaptive probe budget, six diagnostic channels localize where any residual dependence is mediated, component interventions attribute it causally, and the audit returns a confidence-bounded decision with a retain-utility check}{figure.3}{}}
